func TestMockExecutor_RecordsCalls(t *testing.T) {...}
func TestMockExecutor_ReturnsConfiguredOutput(t *testing.T) {...}
func TestMockExecutor_SimulatesError(t *testing.T) {...}
```

## Success Criteria
- MockExecutor in testutil package
- At least 1 run.go function refactored to use it
- Tests demonstrate the pattern works
- Documentation in code comments

